commit.message:
Merge pull request #44 from emonty/master

Stop using distribute
Merge https://github.com/farcepest/MySQLdb1 into merge-upstream

Remove distribute_setup.py reference in MANIFEST

We're not using it anymore, remove the setuptools warning about it not
existing.

Merge pull request #29 from msabramo/tox

Add tox.ini for tox (http://tox.testrun.org/)

Update .travis.yml

It seems Travis no longer supports Python 2.5.

Merge pull request #26 from chipturner/master

Extend read_timeout support to also include write_timeouts

Merge pull request #30 from msabramo/assertEquals

Change one assertTrue to assertEquals to get better failure output

Merge pull request #32 from methane/autocommit

More precise get_autocommit based on server_status.

Merge pull request #34 from tyzhnenko/test-and-fix-issue-33

Fix cut off SQL query when its contained `))`

Merge pull request #35 from methane/static

remove -lmysqlclient when static linking.

Merge pull request #36 from Multiposting/master

Fix the conversion of list or tuple args to SQL.

Merge pull request #38 from olive-oasis/master

microsecond-bug-fix for datetime.datetime

microsecond-bug-fix

When the MySQL Datetime Fraction is less than 6, microseconds set
incorrectly. For example, you set the field, Datetime(3). Then this
library read the time `2013-11-07 10:27:35.705` as `2013-11-08
10:27:35.000705`.
microsecond-bug-fix for datetime.datetime
Also fix executemany().
Syntax fix for python 2.5 support.

Fix the conversion of list or tuple args to a SQL.

When there is one element on the list, the generated SQL was
(1,) (python notation of a single element tuple, which is not
valid in SQL.
remove -lmysqlclient when static linking.

Fix cut off SQL query when its contained `))`, edit insert_values
regexp. Fixes issue #33.
Remove unused variable.
More precise get_autocommit based on server_status.
tox.ini: Add ipdb as a dep because it's very useful for debugging
Change one assertTrue to assertEquals to get better failure output
Add support for tox
Extend read_timeout support to also include write_timeouts

Merge pull request #12 from KLab/autocommit_on

Support keyword argument to initially autocommit=on

Merge pull request #25 from tyzhnenko/microsecond-bug-fix

Fix problem in Datetime with microsecond returns (Issue #24)

Merge pull request #18 from tseaver/do_not_force_distribute

If setuptools is importable, don't force use of 'distribute'.
Fix problem with return None if Datetime field contained microsecond (Issue #24)

Replace raise Error with distutils exception.

Distutils has an exceptions heirarchy. Use it.
